*Computing-work*
Blood dripping from the various cuts on his wrists. Lips pale. Body limp. No sense of remorse or gulit was felt as I starred at the lifeless body in front of me. 
With the scene of blood splashing out of his skin still fresh in my mind, I thought "He was going to get killed anyway," smiling like a chesire cat.
Carrying the limp body of his, I dumped it near a back alleyway and left with blood all over my hands. Time for the next one.
